e a Risk Management Software\">e) Acquire a Risk Management Software<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/bank-tools-and-resources\/#start-your-financial-service-business-today\" title=\"Start Your Financial Service Business Today\">Start Your Financial Service Business Today<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"what-are-the-important-steps-to-follow-when-opening-a-financial-firm\"><\/span>What are the Important Steps to Follow When Opening a Financial Firm?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-create-a-plan-for-your-business\"><\/span>1. Create a Plan for your Business<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Similar to all other businesses, starting up a financial firm require one to have a solid plan. A good plan will assist you in mapping out the details about your banking business and discovering some unknown facts. Your plan must consider some important aspects such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>How much will it cost to start, and what are some of the recurring costs<\/li><li>Who is the target market<\/li><li>How much will you be charging your clients<\/li><li>What name will you give to your financial firm<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Banking is one of the most regulated industries in the world. According to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.forbes.com\/sites\/danschawbel\/2012\/05\/31\/how-to-start-a-business-with-only-100-in-the-bank\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">different reports<\/a>, financial firms may require $12-$20 million as a starting capital. Local banks can raise the money, but they will need to solicit investors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banks mainly target individuals and business owners. Recurring expenses vary depending on the operations of the financial firm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-develop-a-legal-entity\"><\/span>2. Develop a Legal Entity<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are <a href=\"https:\/\/www.forbes.com\/sites\/mikekappel\/2021\/04\/28\/business-structures-101-which-ones-the-best-fit-for-your-company\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">different business structures<\/a> such as sole proprietorship, partnership, and Limited Liability Company and corporation. Establishing a legal business entity as a corporation or LLC protects personal property if one sues your financial firm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/bank-taxes.jpg\" alt=\"bank taxes\" class=\"wp-image-812\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/bank-taxes.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/bank-taxes-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/bank-taxes-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-register-your-financial-firm-for-taxes\"><\/span>3. Register your Financial Firm for Taxes<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before you start operating as a financial firm, you must register your business for different state and federal taxes. Applying for the tax registration identity is easy and free. Some states may require you to pay specific taxes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4-launch-a-financial-firm-bank-account-and-credit-card\"><\/span>4. Launch a Financial Firm Bank Account and Credit Card<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Having a dedicated business bank account and credit card is important for protecting personal assets in case of liabilities. Mixing personal and business accounts puts a risk to your items if you have a court case.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When opening a business account or credit card, <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/\">Verv<\/a> is the best financial firm to choose. Verv is one of the most popular banks that provide a business with exemplary banking services.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5-create-your-business-accounting-system\"><\/span>5. Create your Business Accounting System<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It is important to note down the sources of your income. Recording the different sources of income is important in understanding financial firm financial performance. A good financial record also makes it simple when filing your bank&#8217;s annual return.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6-acquire-the-necessary-permits-and-licenses\"><\/span>6. Acquire the Necessary Permits and Licenses<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Since a financial firm is a business, you should obtain the required licenses and permits. These permits allow you to operate your banking business. Failure to obtain these permits can lead to hefty fines or the risk of closure.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the licenses and permits include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Certificate of occupancy<\/li><li>Local business permit<\/li><li>State licensing requirements<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7-apply-for-financial-firm-insurance\"><\/span>7. Apply for Financial Firm Insurance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Like other businesses, financial firms require an insurance cover to operate safely and lawfully. An insurance cover protects your banking financial wellbeing in case of a covered loss. Banks can apply for different covers that have a variety of risks. Most startups are unaware of the best insurance since they do not know much about the risks involved. Therefore, general liability insurance may be the best cover to start with.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8-develop-your-brand-name\"><\/span>8. Develop your Brand Name<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Your brand is what your financial firm business is all about and how the public perceives it. Having a strong brand will help your bank stand out from the rest. You can promote your brand using different channels such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Developing a good logo<\/li><li>Marketing through different media such as social media, newspapers, and local TV stations<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"9-create-a-business-website\"><\/span>9. Create a Business Website<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After developing your brand, it is important to develop a business website. The business website forms an integral part of any business as it allows potential customers to get more information without necessarily visiting the financial firm. Clients also prefer banks with an official website as it promotes good communication.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-five-main-tools-and-resources-for-running-a-financial-firm\"><\/span>The Five Main Tools and Resources for Running a Financial Firm<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"a-create-a-social-media-account\"><\/span>a) Create a Social Media Account<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Social media is one of the biggest marketing platforms. Having a social media account puts you on top of the list. People on social media are potential clients since they can see the services offered in your financial firm. It will help take your business to a higher level.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"b-provide-online-banking-solutions\"><\/span>b) Provide Online Banking Solutions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Online banking allows people to access financial firm services without necessarily visiting the bank. Online banking capabilities allow banks to take huge steps to offer clients their services. Some of the services provided through online banking include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Fast and easy account creation<\/li><li>Obtaining bank statements<\/li><li>Automated bill payments<\/li><li>Secure message alerts<\/li><li>Access to report and management tools<\/li><li>Desktop software integration<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"c-the-use-of-mobile-apps\"><\/span>c) The use of Mobile Apps<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Setting up a mobile app is important when setting up your financial firm business. Mobile apps provide a great opportunity to grow. Mobile apps allow your <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-multiple-payment-gateways-help-merchants-sell\/#:~:text=Anyone%20looking%20to%20expand%20their%20business%20to%20a%20global%20scale%20should%20consider%20whether%20their%20current%20payment%20provider%20can%20handle%20such%20a%20shift.\">customers to withdraw and deposit money<\/a> without visiting the financial firm. Clients can also pay bills directly from their mobile phones.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"d-budgeting-and-planning-software\"><\/span>d) Budgeting and Planning Software<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It is important to find good software for your budgeting and planning operations. Invest in a good system that can help you save time by integrating the different processes in your financial firm. It will reduce financial frustration and ease the load on employees. Research and choose the best software to use for your normal banking operations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"e-acquire-a-risk-management-software\"><\/span>e) Acquire a Risk Management Software<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Like budgeting and planning software, getting risk management software is crucial. The software will save you lots of time. Performing risk assessment is not easy. Hence, good software will provide incredible results. However, you can outsource such functions to outside companies to help reduce the load on your employees.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"start-your-financial-service-business-today\"><\/span>Start Your Financial Service Business Today<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With the current digital age, it is important to offer banking as a service. Therefore, it is important to consider the type of services to provide to stay relevant in the industry. Ensure that your business goals help you stay afloat and remain active in the highly competitive industry.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most countries are on the verge of launching open financial firm regulations. It shows that the banking sector is moving to an era where clients expect more than just data. It is important to take advantage of these business opportunities before others do when opening your bank. It will help you unlock more business opportunities.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/banking-as-a-service-progress-continues-as-banking-is-made-less-difficult\/\">Banking as a service<\/a> is part of the open financial firm framework that connects different financial services and digital platforms.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The article below provides the main steps, tools, and resources required for running a bank business.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":814,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[16,25,17],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/741"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/w